name: Insurance Money
description:
Finite runner and a kind of survival game.

For some reason, you need to get a lot of money, and you need to get it fast. You got a nice health insurance. Go through this dark alley to get hurt enough to get that juicy insurance money. 

Controls: Move - WASD, Sprint - left Shift, Esc - Pause menu. 

P.S. You need to get at least 10k moneys.
